### Holds API (Staff/Admin)

### Create hold
POST {{baseUrl}}/holds
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventDate": "2026-02-14",
  "tableId": "A09",
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "phone": "+19561231234"
}

###

### List holds for date
GET {{baseUrl}}/holds?eventDate=2026-02-14
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### Release hold
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/holds/2026-03-21/A15
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
